title: An error during ordering the shipping for the Phone repair
content: Hello! I have problems with the display of my Google Pixel 4a and want to repair it but I am in Tbilisi, Georgia at the moment. I was suggested to order shipping by Google Store for repair but on the last step of ordering I get the error ''An unexpected error has occurred. Please try again later. [OR-FGBFDL-25]'. What can I do?
